<item>
            <title>[SEC-71] InteractiveAuthenticationSuccessEvent  should extend AuthenticationEvent</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-71</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;InteractiveAuthenticationSuccessEvent  doesn&apos;t extend AuthenticationEvent. Also, a refactoring is needed to have transparancy between AuthenticationProcessingFilter.onSuccessfulAuthentication and RememberMeServices.loginSuccess, so that when you need to initialize something on successful login, you don&apos;t have to extend 2 classes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12635">SEC-71</key>
            <summary>InteractiveAuthenticationSuccessEvent  should extend AuthenticationEvent</summary>
